                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9383" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0612</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1429 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">双向奔赴之旅：蒙牛集团员工体验项目打造记</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bi-directional Journey: the Exploration of Mengniu Employee Experience</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李亚慧，刘华，郑文丽，麦丽丝，任泽萱，高峰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古蒙牛乳业（集团）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">双向奔赴；员工体验；人力资源数字化；激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bi-directional；employee experience；Digitization of Human Resources；motivation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了蒙牛集团人力资源共享服务中心以数字化技术为依托，在聚焦业务、服务员工的实践中，不断探索并升级员工体验项目的过程。从回顾反思、增加服务价值，到优化完善、提升员工体验感，再到迭代升级、以体验促激励，通过改进员工体验理念、满足工作-生活多方位体验需求、构建完整的体系来优化和升级员工体验项目，打造职业生涯全周期的专属与幸福，激发员工的组织承诺度与归属感，进而促进工作绩效，实现数字化技术赋能员工体验的提升。通过本案例教学，帮助学生理解和掌握员工体验在激励过程中的关键作用，引导学生利用相关激励理论分析员工体验和解决人力资源服务价值的实际问题，帮助学生更好地理解企业如何依托数字技术打造员工体验项目，实现员工发展与企业目标一致的“双向奔赴”之旅。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the process by which Mengniu Human Resources Sharing Service Center, leveraging digital technology, continuously explores and upgrades employee experience in its practice of focusing on business and serving employees. From reviewing and reflecting on improving service value, to optimizing and improving employee experience, and then to iteratively upgrading and driving incentive effects through experience, Mengniu HRSSC optimizes and upgrades employee experience projects by optimizing the concept of &quot;employee experience&quot;, meeting the multi-dimensional experience needs of work-life, and building a systematic system. Meanwhile, it can also create exclusivity and happiness for employees throughout their career cycle, stimulate their organizational commitment and sense of belonging. Finally, it will promote the work performance, achieving the enhancement of employee experience through digital technology empowerment. This case aims to help students understand and master the key role of employee experience in the motivation process, guiding them to use relevant motivation theories to analyze employee experience and solve practical problems of human resource service value. Finally, it will help students in better understanding how enterprises can leverage digital technology to build employee experience projects and achieve value co-creation between employees and enterprise through a &quot;journey of mutual commitment&quot; .</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《薪酬管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源数字化转型；员工激励；客户体验；员工体验；全面报酬体系</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
